        </section>
        <p data-uuid="fc58c55a7a2e43f6994d5e66688f8437">Texas agreed to give up its land claims in New Mexico in exchange for financial aid from the federal government. The compromise outlawed the slave trade in the District of Columbia and established a new fugitive slave law.<br />
        </p>
